---
title: Sticky Sweet-Soy Beef Tacos with Asian Slaw & Sriracha Mayo
description: Sometimes it can be tricky to find new ways to jazz up tacos but not tonight - onion chutney on beef is taking out the guesswork
and creating new inspiration for your taco night. We also threw a herby mayo into the slaw for a bit of fun.

